  "title": "EVENTSCREW/BRAND AMBASSADOR",
  "description": "<p><strong>What You’ll Do:</strong></p><p></p><ul><li><strong>Be the frontline ambassador for reputable partner</strong> brands at events and roadshows</li></ul><ul><li><strong>Confidently engage customers </strong>and clearly communicate how the brand’s services improve their lives</li></ul><p></p><ul><li><strong>Turn meaningful conversations into successful sign-ups </strong>and smooth onboardings.</li></ul><p></p><ul><li>Collaborate with a <strong>motivated</strong>, <strong>performance-driven</strong> team to execute campaigns and exceed targets.</li></ul><p></p><ul><li>Create <strong>positive</strong>, <strong>memorable customer experiences</strong> that build long-term trust and brand loyalty</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Why You’ll Want This Role</strong></p><p></p><ul><li><strong>Weekly payouts every Friday –</strong> fast, transparent, and reliable income.</li></ul><p></p><ul><li><strong>No experience needed – </strong>full one-to-one training, proven scripts, and hands-on coaching provided.</li></ul><p></p><ul><li>A <strong>high-energy,</strong> <strong>supportive team culture</strong> where effort is recognised and rewarded.</li></ul><p></p><ul><li><strong>Referral incentives – </strong>earn extra by bringing friends into the team.</li></ul><ul><li><strong>Regular team bonding</strong> and social events (KBBQ, hotpot, laser tag, KTV, and more).</li></ul><p></p><ul><li><strong>Exclusive gym membership</strong> to support your health, confidence, and lifestyle.</li></ul><p></p><ul><li><strong>Clear pathways to leadership roles</strong>, career advancement, and overseas exposure.</li></ul><p></p><p><u><em><strong>This is not just a job. Many team members start on the ground and advance into team lead, trainer, or management roles based purely on performance—not seniority.</strong></em></u></p><p></p><p><strong>Who Excels Here:</strong></p><ul><li>You <strong>enjoy meeting new people</strong> and building rapport quickly</li></ul><ul><li>You have a <strong>positive</strong>, <strong>coachable mindset </strong>and are eager to learn</li></ul><ul><li>You want <strong>strong income</strong> and <strong>real personal growth</strong>, <em>not just a routine role</em></li></ul><ul><li>You are <strong>motivated</strong>, <strong>disciplined</strong>, and <strong>goal-oriented</strong></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Basic Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li> 18 years and above</li></ul><ul><li>Singapore Citizen or Permanent Resident (PR)</li></ul><ul><li>Minimum 3-month commitment</li></ul><ul><li>Able to work 5–6 days per week (day shifts)</li></ul><p></p><p></p>",
